text: "2 Faced" is a song recorded by English singer Louise which was released as on 17 July 2000, as the lead single from Louise's third studio album Elbow Beach (2000). It is her highest charting single to date, reaching number three in the UK Singles Chart. ==Track listings== UK CD 1 single #"2 Faced" #"Say Yes" #"Lost" #"2 Faced" video UK CD 2 single #"2 Faced" #"2 Faced" (Agnelli & Nelson Vocal mix) #"2 Faced" (Perfect Phase Vocal) ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:Louise Redknapp songs Category:Pop songs Category:Hip hop soul songs Category:R&B; songs
